@startuml
title 会话状态机
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Discovered
Discovered --> Handshaking : SessionHello
Handshaking --> Authenticated : SessionAuthenticate 成功
Handshaking --> Closed : 认证失败
Authenticated --> Negotiated : SessionCapabilities 接受
Negotiated --> Active : SessionReady + major 匹配
Negotiated --> Closed : major 不匹配
Active --> Draining : transport 断连\n或主动收尾
Draining --> Closed : 清理完成
Active --> Closed : 显式关闭
Closed --> [*]
@enduml
